\subsubsection{The warrior skill only operates when the warrior is engaged; this
is when they are occupying an opponent's melee zone.}
a36 10
Note to find the requirements for any given Rank find the Rank in the
first column and read across the row noting requirements in each
column. Thus to achieve a given Rank a warrior must have at least one
weapon of the minimum Rank (given in the minimum Rank column) in at
least as many categories as given in the no. categories column
(categories refers to the weapon categories assigned in the attached
list of weapons).  In addition the warrior must have weapons of higher
Rank as noted in the other columns.


